text: Aadorf is a municipality of the district of Münchwilen in the canton of Thurgau in Switzerland. With a population of 7,436 people (as of 2005), it is the canton's seventh largest municipality. == References == == Other websites == *Official website of Aadorf *Website of Guntershausen *Website of Ettenhausen *Website of Wittenwil Category:Municipalities in Münchwilen
